column2: SELECT G.objID, G.ra, G.dec, G.specObjID, G.type, Z.z, Z.zErr, SP.z, SP.zErr into mydb.t5#_mytable from PhotoObjAll as G FROM MyDB.MyTable AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.RA, m.dec, #) AS GN ON G.objID = GN.objID AND G.type = # JOIN PhotoZ AS Z ON G.ObjID = Z.ObjID JOIN SpecObjAll AS SP ON G.specObjID = SP.specObjID
